Boha, který odpouští za zlaťáky. Tu jde spíše o kruh, cyklus, který se musí
završit, protože příroda taková je.

Něco v tomto smyslu:
Actually and sadly for everyone, no one gets away with doing bad things,
meaning hurting others. The universe dont require you to help another, but
doing so removes karmic dept owed. So in effect to help another is to help
oneself. And the reverse is true, that to do harm causes karmic dept, meaning
to hurt another is to hurt one self. The reason this is true is as old as the
ancient teachings known about long ago. All energy sent out must return home.
This is the great circle, and everything is the circle. Even energy and
magnetism must obey this law, as everything in the universe must. Oddly its
one of the reasons I like batteries as such a simple thing displays the laws
of the universe in itself, but then everything does really. Every thing is
circular from the larger view of it all, everything is a repeat as well which
also represents the great circle. If you have not noticed the world is round,
so is the solar system and the galaxy. It all spins, it all repeats, it all
comes around again. Even the atoms are circular and repeat in their
connections to other atoms, same with molecules, the same with planets going
around their suns or moons around their planets, to the view of the stars in
the heavens. Have you not noticed even time is a repeat from seconds to
minutes to hours to days and years. Even nature, and its seasons to the
weather is a repeat which means circular even if it dont seem quite so round,
in erratic repeats, its still circular none the less and a repeat. The great
circle is the simplest fundamental law of the universe and must be expressed
in all things, and in time always is. So the energy you send out or use to do
bad things or harm another must return home or come around again back to you
to complete the circle, even if not in this reincarnation that energy will
return. This is a universal law and again expressed in everything, you have
only to look about to see it in the atoms, nature, time, energy, the universe
as this law is expressed in and through everything and is an absolute.&#65279;
